          "date": "2017-04-17 21:13:00.000000000",
          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-8653 lod: use stripe_count instead of stripe_nr",
        "message": "LU-8653 lod: use stripe_count instead of stripe_nr\n\nReplace the use of stripenr in the code with stripe_count so that\nthis is consistent with this field name in the rest of the code.\n\nIntroduce LOV_PATTERN_NONE instead of using \"0\" around the code to\nindicate no layout has been specified.\n\nIntroduce LOV_PATTERN_DEFAULT to indicate that the entire layout is\nunset, instead of using \"0xffffffff\" explicitly in the code.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I6056aebc1a381b09c1a436fb4a7986a51f5a0c30\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
